#: templates/public/about.html:80
msgid "About Weilight Harbor"
msgstr "关于微光港湾"

#: templates/public/about.html:81
msgid ""
"A warm digital harbor for caregivers and families navigating the journey "
"of serious illness. Here, no one walks alone."
msgstr ""
"一个为照护者和重病家庭打造的温暖数字港湾。在这里，没有人独行。"

#: templates/public/about.html:89
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "我们的使命"

#: templates/public/about.html:91
msgid ""
"Weilight Harbor was born from a simple belief: caregivers and families "
"facing serious illness deserve a safe space to share, connect, and find "
"support. We provide a platform where empathy flows freely, where stories "
"illuminate the path for others, and where practical help is always within"
" reach."
msgstr ""
"微光港湾源于一个简单的信念：照护者和面对重病的家庭值得拥有一个安全的空间来"
"分享、连接和寻求支持。我们提供一个让关怀自由流动的平台，在这里，故事为他人"
"照亮前路，实际的帮助触手可及。"

#: templates/public/about.html:101
msgid "Our Values"
msgstr "我们的价值观"

#: templates/public/about.html:108
msgid "Compassion"
msgstr "关怀"

#: templates/public/about.html:109
msgid ""
"Every interaction is grounded in empathy and understanding. We listen "
"without judgment and support without conditions."
msgstr ""
"每一次互动都建立在共情和理解之上。我们倾听而不评判，支持而不附加条件。"

#: templates/public/about.html:117
msgid "Safety"
msgstr "安全"

#: templates/public/about.html:118
msgid ""
"This is a safe harbor. We protect privacy, moderate content sensitively, "
"and maintain a space free from harm."
msgstr ""
"这是一个安全的港湾。我们保护隐私，审慎地管理内容，维护一个远离伤害的空间。"

#: templates/public/about.html:127
msgid ""
"Strength comes from connection. We bring together families, volunteers, "
"and organizations to form a caring community."
msgstr ""
"力量源于连接。我们将家庭、志愿者和组织聚集在一起，形成一个关爱的社区。"

#: templates/public/about.html:139 templates/public/index.html:53
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "如何使用"

#: templates/public/about.html:143
msgid "Create an Account"
msgstr "创建账号"

#: templates/public/about.html:144
msgid ""
"Sign up for free and join our community. Optionally get certified to "
"unlock more features."
msgstr ""
"免费注册并加入我们的社区。可选择进行认证以解锁更多功能。"

#: templates/public/about.html:150
msgid "Connect and Share"
msgstr "连接与分享"

#: templates/public/about.html:151
msgid ""
"Share your story in the community, keep a private life journal, or find "
"support at the respite station."
msgstr ""
"在社区分享你的故事，记录私密的生命手账，或在喘息驿站寻求支持。"

#: templates/public/about.html:157
msgid "Give and Receive Help"
msgstr "互助互援"

#: templates/public/about.html:158
msgid ""
"Launch or support crowdfunding campaigns, volunteer your time, or simply "
"be there for someone who needs it."
msgstr ""
"发起或支持众筹项目，奉献你的时间做志愿者，或者只是陪伴需要帮助的人。"

#: templates/public/about.html:171
msgid "Our Team"
msgstr "我们的团队"

#: templates/public/about.html:173
msgid ""
"Weilight Harbor is built by a small team of designers, developers, and "
"social workers who have been personally touched by the caregiving "
"journey. We understand the challenges because we have lived them. Every "
"feature is crafted with real needs in mind."
msgstr ""
"微光港湾由一支小型团队打造，成员包括设计师、开发者和社工，他们都亲身经历过"
"照护之路。我们理解这些挑战，因为我们亲身走过。每一个功能都是基于真实需求精"
"心设计的。"

#: templates/public/about.html:176
msgid "Join the Community"
msgstr "加入社区"

#: templates/public/about.html:177
msgid "Get Help"
msgstr "获取帮助"

#: templates/public/help.html:2 templates/public/help.html:70
msgid "Help Center"
msgstr "帮助中心"

#: templates/public/help.html:71
msgid "Find answers to common questions about using Weilight Harbor."
msgstr "查找关于使用微光港湾的常见问题解答。"

#: templates/public/help.html:82
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "开始使用"

#: templates/public/help.html:88
msgid "How do I create an account?"
msgstr "如何创建账号？"

#: templates/public/help.html:93
msgid ""
"Click \"Join the Harbor\" in the top navigation bar. Fill in your "
"username, email, and password. After registration, you will be "
"automatically logged in and can start using all basic features right "
"away."
msgstr ""
"点击顶部导航栏中的\"加入港湾\"。填写您的用户名、邮箱和密码。注册后，您将自"
"动登录，并可以立即开始使用所有基本功能。"

#: templates/public/help.html:100
msgid "What is certification and do I need it?"
msgstr "什么是认证？我需要认证吗？"

#: templates/public/help.html:105
msgid ""
"Certification verifies your identity as a family caregiver or volunteer. "
"While not required for basic features like browsing and posting, "
"certification unlocks advanced features such as creating crowdfunding "
"campaigns and builds trust within the community. You can apply from your "
"profile page."
msgstr ""
"认证可以验证您作为家庭照护者或志愿者的身份。虽然浏览和发帖等基本功能不需要"
"认证，但认证可以解锁创建众筹项目等高级功能，并在社区中建立信任。您可以在个"
"人主页中申请认证。"

#: templates/public/help.html:112
msgid "Is the platform free to use?"
msgstr "平台免费使用吗？"

#: templates/public/help.html:117
msgid ""
"Yes, Weilight Harbor is completely free for all users. We are a non-"
"profit platform dedicated to helping caregivers and families. All "
"donations through crowdfunding go directly to the campaign recipients."
msgstr ""
"是的，微光港湾对所有用户完全免费。我们是一个致力于帮助照护者和家庭的非营利"
"平台。通过众筹的所有捐助都将直接到达筹款项目的接收人。"

#: templates/public/help.html:132
msgid "How do I create a post?"
msgstr "如何发帖？"

#: templates/public/help.html:137
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Community page and click \"Create Post.\" You can share "
"your experiences, ask questions, or offer support. Posts are moderated to"
" keep the community safe and respectful."
msgstr ""
"进入社区页面并点击\"发帖\"。您可以分享经历、提出问题或提供支持。帖子会经过审"
"核，以确保社区的安全和尊重。"

#: templates/public/help.html:144
msgid "Can I post anonymously?"
msgstr "我可以匿名发帖吗？"

#: templates/public/help.html:149
msgid ""
"Yes, you can choose to post anonymously when creating a post. Anonymous "
"posts will show a generic username to protect your privacy while still "
"allowing you to share and connect."
msgstr ""
"可以，您在发帖时可以选择匿名发布。匿名帖子会显示通用用户名，以保护您的隐私"
"，同时仍然允许您分享和互动。"

#: templates/public/help.html:164
msgid "How do I start a crowdfunding campaign?"
msgstr "如何发起众筹项目？"

#: templates/public/help.html:169
msgid ""
"You need to be a certified user to create a campaign. Once certified, go "
"to the Crowdfunding page and click \"Create Campaign.\" Fill in the "
"details about the patient, the funding goal, and your story. Campaigns "
"are reviewed before going live."
msgstr ""
"您需要成为认证用户才能创建筹款项目。认证后，前往众筹页面并点击\"创建筹款项目"
"\"。填写患者的详细信息、筹款目标和您的故事。项目在上线前会经过审核。"

#: templates/public/help.html:176
msgid "How are funds distributed?"
msgstr "资金如何分配？"

#: templates/public/help.html:181
msgid ""
"This is a demo platform. In a production environment, funds would be "
"transferred directly to the verified recipient after the campaign ends or"
" when withdrawal is requested. All transactions would be transparent and "
"auditable."
msgstr ""
"这是一个演示平台。在正式环境中，资金将在筹款项目结束后或申请提现时直接转给"
"经过验证的接收人。所有交易都将透明且可审计。"

#: templates/public/help.html:190
msgid "Account & Privacy"
msgstr "账户与隐私"

#: templates/public/help.html:196
msgid "How is my personal information protected?"
msgstr "我的个人信息如何受到保护？"

#: templates/public/help.html:201
msgid ""
"We take privacy seriously. Personal information submitted during "
"certification is encrypted and only accessible to authorized reviewers. "
"We never share your data with third parties. See our Privacy Policy for "
"full details."
msgstr ""
"我们非常重视隐私保护。认证过程中提交的个人信息会被加密，且仅授权审核人员可"
"以访问。我们绝不会与第三方共享您的数据。详情请参阅我们的隐私政策。"

#: templates/public/help.html:208
msgid "How do I reset my password?"
msgstr "如何重置密码？"

#: templates/public/help.html:213
msgid ""
"Click \"Forgot password?\" on the login page and enter your registered "
"email address. You will receive a password reset link. Note: this is a "
"demo feature in the current version."
msgstr ""
"在登录页面点击\"忘记密码？\"，然后输入您注册时使用的邮箱地址。您将收到一个密"
"码重置链接。注意：在当前版本中这是一个演示功能。"

#: templates/public/help.html:222
msgid "Still need help?"
msgstr "仍需帮助？"

#: templates/public/help.html:223
msgid ""
"If you could not find an answer to your question, feel free to reach out "
"to our support team."
msgstr ""
"如果您未能找到问题的答案，请随时联系我们的支持团队。"

