#: templates/public/privacy.html:52 templates/public/terms.html:52
msgid "Last updated"
msgstr "最后更新"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:60
msgid ""
"At Weilight Harbor, your privacy is of utmost importance to us. This "
"Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, protect, and share your "
"personal information when you use our platform."
msgstr ""
"在微光港湾，您的隐私对我们至关重要。本隐私政策说明了当您使用我们的平台时，"
"我们如何收集、使用、保护和共享您的个人信息。"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:62
msgid "Information We Collect"
msgstr "我们收集的信息"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:63
msgid "We collect the following types of information:"
msgstr "我们收集以下类型的信息："

#: templates/public/privacy.html:65
msgid "Account Information"
msgstr "账户信息"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:65
msgid "Username, email address, and password when you register."
msgstr "注册时的用户名、邮箱地址和密码。"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:66
msgid "Profile Information"
msgstr "个人资料信息"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:66
msgid "Optional details such as your real name, phone number, bio, and avatar."
msgstr "可选的详细信息，如真实姓名、电话号码、个人简介和头像。"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:67
msgid "Certification Data"
msgstr "认证数据"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:67
msgid ""
"Identity documents, patient information, and medical records submitted "
"for certification."
msgstr ""
"为认证而提交的身份证件、患者信息和医疗记录。"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:68
msgid "Usage Data"
msgstr "使用数据"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:68
msgid ""
"Information about how you interact with our platform, including pages "
"visited and features used."
msgstr ""
"关于您如何与我们平台互动的信息，包括访问的页面和使用的功能。"

#: templates/public/community/create_post.html:255
#: templates/public/privacy.html:69
msgid "Content"
msgstr "内容"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:69
msgid ""
"Posts, comments, journal entries, and other content you create on the "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"您在平台上创建的帖子、评论、手账记录和其他内容。"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:72
msgid "How We Use Your Information"
msgstr "我们如何使用您的信息"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:74
msgid "To provide, maintain, and improve our services"
msgstr "提供、维护和改进我们的服务"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:75
msgid "To verify your identity during the certification process"
msgstr "在认证过程中验证您的身份"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:76
msgid "To facilitate crowdfunding campaigns and donations"
msgstr "促进众筹项目和捐助"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:77
msgid "To communicate with you about your account and our services"
msgstr "就您的账户和我们的服务与您沟通"

#: templates/public/privacy.html:78
